# Web3Forms access key for the contact form.
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com and enter your email (nicolebernardo96@gmail.com).
# 2. Copy the Access Key they email you.
# 3. Copy this file to `.env.local` and paste the key below.
# Vite only exposes vars prefixed with VITE_ to the client.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your_access_key_here
